</div>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-background">Welcome back, DROPBEST!</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-stack-sm">Manage your platform confirmations and activities.</p>
</section>
